{"tid":1532942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知大家有冇啲懶係黃既屋企人","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:17:41.000Z","uid":135959,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1f2ff2ff6666fc2dea331f21052f05e2594b05","tid":1532942,"uid":135959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:42:42.000Z","msg":"小弟year 3 <br />\n<br />\n69 開始已經出去，當時佢自稱黃，開頭都冇咩野，621 圍警總嗰日佢屌9我，同佢嘈咗好撚柒耐，之後我索性呃尻佢算。<br />\n<br />\n佢成日屌啲黑警乜乜物物，又話佢地會有報應，但另一方面日日叫我咪撚去集會，even 係和理非既遊行，佢都會俾説話我聽。<br />\n<br />\n講真，真係好撚辛苦，全家得我係對政治有反應，老豆就唔撚洗講，成尻日話搞亂，香港已經好自由，根本大家價值觀都唔同，所以唔會改變到佢地個垃圾思想。<br />\n<br />\n我本係一個好撚冷靜理性既人，純粹想揾個渠道發泄吓，人都癲，好大無力感"},{"pid":"f741f638b084588a183667bfed70564f8db209c6","tid":1532942,"uid":135959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人都係咁，個個禮拜都要諗啲理由"},{"pid":"130afea546e92e9b1e1c9242931ddbc15d440ffa","tid":1532942,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:43:51.000Z","msg":"往好處諗 總好過藍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b052dbc14d9be9bdfeb29a78e822d2c3ef31483b","tid":1532942,"uid":264091,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:44:49.000Z","msg":"我屋企都係咁<br />\n但佢地係出於擔心<br />\n只要番到屋企比到個交代就無事"},{"pid":"97aa915213717df72ed691f75b8dce95d6b377ca","tid":1532942,"uid":41658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"其實都係驚你出事，香港人係咁自私"},{"pid":"759ed3de0b9469703ad078fceb6e4e49859d81eb","tid":1532942,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"邊度似黃"},{"pid":"70c07c58fc56aeaa54bb1ce2515b1655ea39a51c","tid":1532942,"uid":283136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:46:08.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/A5txahW6h5rSiBAiz5z2XA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FA5txahW6h5rSiBAiz5z2XA&d=aS0Zid